 et en couleurs de quatre m\u00e9daillons oblongs \u00e0 vues de ports de mer avec personnages v\u00eatus \u00e0 l\u0027orientale, alternant avec des rinceaux et des quadrill\u00e9s. revers orn\u00e9 de 3 bouquets de fleurs. Fond de jet\u00e9es de fleurs polychromes","inscriptions":"Marque de l\u0027atelier : \r ; Deux \u00e9p\u00e9es entrecrois\u00e9es peintes en bleu (Sur le pot \u00e0 oille et sur le plateau)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"19","displayDimension":"19 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"22","displayDimension":"22 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"16","displayDimension":"16 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":8,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":9,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"29,5","displayDimension":"29,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":10,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : porcelaine dure\r\nTechnique : techniques c\u00e9ramique","placeOfCreation":"Meissen = Mei\u00dfen (Allemagne-\u003ESaxe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Legs \u00c9lise Dosne-Thiers, 1880, sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit de sa s\u0153ur F\u00e9licie Dosne qui y renonce et ex\u00e9cute le legs en 1881.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Dosne-Thiers, Elise","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027arriv\u00e9e au Mus\u00e9e","value":"1881","startYear":1881,"endYear":1881}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des 